to Hong Kong or China for your career?

424
00:41:39,680 --> 00:41:41,280
If the opportunity arises.

425
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:43,960
But my family is here,

426
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:46,320
and I want us to be together.

427
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:50,400
I hear you hole up somewhere for months
when you're working on your art.

428
00:41:50,480 --> 00:41:52,840
Does that break your heart, Mr. Sun?

429
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:55,440
Of course, it does.

430
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:57,480
She holed up in her workshop

431
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:59,160
for three months to work on this project.

432
00:41:59,240 --> 00:42:00,720
For three months, I had no wife.

433
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:05,720
I've repressed this inspiration
for four years,

434
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,840
and now, it is surging
like a wave I cannot ignore.

435
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:11,320
I'm lucky that my husband and son
are supportive of me.

436
00:42:12,480 --> 00:42:15,720
My family are not the only ones
I must thank for this solo exhibition.

437
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:18,400
I'm also thankful for my sponsor,

438
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:20,920
philanthropist Deng Wanhao.

439
00:42:22,280 --> 00:42:23,760
For every piece sold,

440
00:42:23,840 --> 00:42:27,800
Mr. Deng will donate $100,000 to UNICEF.

441
00:42:29,200 --> 00:42:31,080
That's enough from me.

442
00:42:31,160 --> 00:42:33,800
Let me unveil the main piece of the night.

443
00:43:04,920 --> 00:43:06,080
My artwork is entitled…

444
00:43:06,880 --> 00:43:08,520
<i>Who Killed Sera?</i>

445
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:11,200
In commemoration of my daughter, Sera,

446
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:13,160
who died four years ago.

447
00:43:14,320 --> 00:43:18,560
She died on February 29, 2020.

448
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:22,080
On the same day in 2016,

449
00:43:22,160 --> 00:43:25,600
another woman named Xie Liping
was also dismembered.

450
00:43:26,120 --> 00:43:27,720
It's been so many years,

451
00:43:27,800 --> 00:43:30,000
but the police
still haven't caught the Leap Day Killer.

452
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:35,000
I hope this immoral killer sees my art.

453
00:43:35,080 --> 00:43:37,400
I hope they feel a mother's pain

454
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:39,160
and turn themselves in.

